      <p>
        {{ ABBR }} Racer is a retro-styled arcade racing minigame made for
        {{ COMPANY_FULLNAME }}. It is heavily inspired by <em>Outrun,</em> with
        similar faux-3D effects and sprite scaling. Race through the Arizona
        desert in {{ COMPANY_FULLNAME }}&rsquo;s
        <a
          href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nissan_GT-R"
          target="_blank"
          title="cue eurobeat"
          >GT-R</a
        >
        and reach the goal in the time limit.
      </p>
