      <p>
        Here&rsquo;s a fun little fact about the game: You can unlock a hidden
        hard mode if you beat the game without hitting any cars on the road or
        crashing. If you successfully do that, upon restarting the game
        you&rsquo;ll see you&rsquo;re playing as
        <q title="An inside joke from the company at the time">Terry Turbo</q>
        and the game will have slightly different stats: the car&rsquo;s top
        speed, acceleration, and handling will all increase, but the time limit
        will decrease. And higher speed means you&rsquo;re more likely to run
        off the track after hitting an opponent driver!
      </p>
